LAST 6 HOURS AT HINDI PA RIN KAMI PAGOD MAG-BEG‼️🔱

Hey Psych Tams! Still looking for an organization to join? Kung sino-sino pang hinahanap mo eh nandito naman na ang Legal and Legislative Department ng FEU Psychology Society para sa'yo!⚖️

Interested sa pagreview ng legal docs? Or baka naman favorite past time ang panonood ng senate sessions? 

We are open to all psych students regardless of experience! Tutulungan at gagabayan namin kayo every step of the way🤗

Kaya apply na!

https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership 
https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership 
https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership

message.text:
LAST 6 HOURS AT HINDI PA RIN KAMI PAGOD MAG-BEG‼️🔱

Hey Psych Tams! Still looking for an organization to join? Kung sino-sino pang hinahanap mo eh nandito naman na ang Legal and Legislative Department ng FEU Psychology Society para sa'yo!⚖️

Interested sa pagreview ng legal docs? Or baka naman favorite past time ang panonood ng senate sessions? 

We are open to all psych students regardless of experience! Tutulungan at gagabayan namin kayo every step of the way🤗

Kaya apply na!

https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership 
https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership 
https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership
